{"tid":2250181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【突發！！！】留任派將重整旗於立法會議會戰線作出全面反擊準備，力阻大灣區「境外投票」！！！！","createTime":"2020-10-20T02:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T07:35:29.000Z","uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"90b43251e4507c7aaf19f5680d0a9e436d8b6dc2","tid":2250181,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20201019/s00002/1603045085507/力阻「境外投票」-胡志偉倡三線作戰</code></pre><br />\n睇黎呢場戰役蓄勢待發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】民主黨主席胡志偉上月底接任民主派召集人。港府計劃修例於內地設票站，讓內地港人於下屆立法會選舉投票，胡志偉料特首林鄭月娥將「不惜一切代價」推行計劃，<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">籲以「3條戰線」阻撓項目</span></span></strong>，稱會考慮爭取國際關注等。他說民主派來年「不是與民為敵，只是與政府為敵」，惟《港區國安法》下議會抗爭成本增加，<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">他質疑議員應否「隨隨便便送頭」，認為要以「符合比例」的抗爭態度應對各個場景。</span></strong></span><br />\n明報記者 張彤<br />\n難只靠議會阻法案 冀與國際街頭並行<br />\n<br />\n內地港人投票爭議不斷，胡志偉上周接受本報專訪時認為，政府為徹底消滅民主派取過半議席（35+）的機會，必定會全力推行計劃。他稱不能光靠議會阻撓法案通過，<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">「常說3條戰線，但當要貶低議會功能時，就會覺得國際戰線和街頭抗爭很重要，但事實上它們是互相補充」</span></span></strong>。他說會考慮爭取國際關注、與民陣等團體合作，以達至國際、街頭、議會戰線並行。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">不應隨便送頭 「合適抗爭」應對不同場景</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n本月初立法會內會、財會主席選舉，民主派多番提名及提出規程問題，沒有出現激烈的議會衝突場面。《港區國安法》訂明，「嚴重干擾、阻撓、破壞特區政權機關依法履行職能」觸及顛覆國家政權罪，<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">胡志偉質疑，議員應否「隨隨便便去送頭？國安法只不過令你選擇一個更符合比例的手法處理（事情）」</span></span></strong>，解釋要以合適的抗爭態度應對不同場景。<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">隨着朱凱廸、陳志全離任，非建制議員減至21人，胡稱在人力有限下，處事應更深思熟慮，「我們現在不是爭相做英雄」；但他認同市民有不同的期望，「無論我們怎麼做，都一定不能盡如人意」。</span></span></strong><br />\n可支持惠民議案 「非與民為敵」<br />\n<br />\n陳志全早前表示，今年度的立法會是非法議會，留任議員應盡數否決所有項目。胡志偉強調民主派「不是與民為敵，只是與政府為敵」，對於全民派錢、興建學校及醫院等直接惠民項目，他認為民主派可以支持，因能減少政府「為惡」的本錢。他解釋，在抗爭運動中「不能讓政府肥，要讓它瘦下去」，故民主派投票時會考慮政策會否擴大政府的權力。<br />\n暫擬與素人「議題形式」合作<br />\n<br />\n民主派上月決定留任，並稱會與初選素人商討合作平台，胡志偉說，民主黨許智峯、公民黨譚文豪等議員均已與素人聯絡，目前希望涵蓋區議會素人、上次立法會選舉的參選人；平台初步打算以議題形式（project-based）運作，內容包括明日大嶼、內地設票站等，希望參與者運用自身影響力鼓勵公衆介入議題。至於平台所涉及的人力、物力等資源，胡志偉說「可能大一點的share（承擔）來自我們，小一點的share來自其他朋友」，但強調資源問題屬次要。被問類似反修訂《逃犯條例》的議會衝突會否在來年重演，胡志偉稱「我不會每一件事、每一個場景都和過去比較，但我肯定所有同事均預料，在未來一年面對愈來愈高的檢控風險」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">我係林鄭既話，而家一定淆底淆到震，震撚過貓王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映<strong><span class=\"violet\">香港之光黃世澤</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KJhgKQNKJoM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKJhgKQNKJoM&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=5970f40f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KJhgKQNKJoM</a><br />\n<strong><span class=\"violet\">佢話中西區區議會成功成立獨立秘書處，可以培養黃營政治人材，黃色民官體系，為成立臨時政府借殼上市做準備，一個屈尾十仲可以搞埋香港獨立，好似愛爾蘭咁</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">佢仲反指之前叫人唔好打議會戰線既焦土派，根本就係幫中共做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港民主制度就係俾呢Ｄ玩死，香港就係要清除呢Ｄ內奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n同埋成班道德撚道德去到喜馬拉亞山咁高，最終只會一事無成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">美軍如果攻入黎，都要有文官帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地香港人欠民主黨一個ＣＲＥＤＩＴ呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N9itpBqgDrc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DN9itpBqgDrc&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=fc5356f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N9itpBqgDrc</a><br />\n老蕭呢Ｄ咁樣屌民主黨，居心可測<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死內奸蕭若源<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jMNaHGh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjMNaHGh.gif&h=e4bf2e75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd5e0ad4de4f4885ec340328fe8cd67c708a4c19","tid":2250181,"uid":273703,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c001f6f833ad5d331f59e0fddd8304b411a0be4d","tid":2250181,"uid":1654,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"扮乜鳩議會有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2de9141fcb76478e2940b2dd4e0c086c95a493f","tid":2250181,"uid":88743,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c001f6f833ad5d331f59e0fddd8304b411a0be4d","tid":2250181,"uid":1654,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"扮乜鳩議會有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"世澤話有用<br />\n你敢話無用？<br />\n你係咪其中一個內奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7c0fd5f533faba618953036ce4b25e860b0ec5","tid":2250181,"uid":10056,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:57:16.000Z","msg":"覺得佢地真係好可悲 明知無用俾人當空氣 都要入去叫口號舉牌 有用既總辭又唔肯做 唉 小醜咁"},{"pid":"35dc7d75b64aeeab2c6bd8ce50a8bb5bd532420f","tid":2250181,"uid":226622,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:59:29.000Z","msg":"<del>留任派</del> 花瓶派"},{"pid":"7d432e3344a80b3525c28f4c0b86b3961ccef634","tid":2250181,"uid":317956,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"基本上可以用一個人就阻成個議會幾個月，佢地怕死者"},{"pid":"cf3b339ded629407056626605cb00fda543928a8","tid":2250181,"uid":276191,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"想點反擊呀, 睇過!"},{"pid":"ad0c47e1023fad4545428f668e764fa68a80a328","tid":2250181,"uid":134323,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0